These remain subject to the original license in LICENSE.txt.

Derivative work
---------------
ElvQuestButton — ElvUI integration and extended feature set
Copyright (c) 2024-2026 Sherlockell

Additions by Sherlockell include (non-exhaustive): the ElvUI skin/integration
module (ElvUI/), the LibEditMode standalone fallback (standalone.lua), the
lock/switch and soft-select item handling, the item-count badge, artwork
background layering with size/rotation controls, font customization, and the
movement-aware update scheduling.

